data.description: Great New Price! Welcome home to this beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in the desirable Gramercy Farms community. This like-new home is move-in ready and features amazing upgrades throughout! As you enter the foyer, you’re brought into the open concept space with the living room up front. The stone accent wall encased between 2 large windows is the perfect accent space and focal point of the room. As you move back into the home, you’re welcomed into the dining room and kitchen. Dark cabinetry, quartz countertops, and stainless-steel appliances elevate this space with sliding glass doors leading you directly outside. Off the hallway are all 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms with the primary bedroom tucked up at the back. This room offers a walk-in closet plus an amazing ensuite with double sink vanity and glass front stand up shower. Make your way outside to find the perfect, fully fenced green space of your dreams! Schedule your private showing today, you won’t want to miss out on the opportunity to call this “home”!
